    • Uses of JContext in gdt.jgui.base

      Classes in gdt.jgui.base that implement JContext 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  JAllCategoriesPanel
      This context displays a list of all categories (types of entities).
      class  JBaseNavigator
      This context displays items for database navigation: Design - show the general-purpose control for low-level database management Search - show the search control to find an entity by label All categories - display the all categories list.
      class  JBasesPanel
      This context displays all databases located in the given directory.
      class  JCategoryPanel
      This context displays of all entities belonging to the category.
      class  JContainerPanel
      This context displays actions to manage container/component relations : Exclude - to exclude component from the container List components - to list all components of the container Facets - display the facets context for the container.
      class  JDesignPanel
      This class displays the general-purpose low-level database management control.
      class  JPropertyPanel
      This context displays actions to manage property names: Add property - to add a property name Delete - to delete the property name.
      class  JValuePanel
      This context displays actions to manage property values: Add value - to add a property value Delete - to delete the property value.
